How to set-up EpSentinel working on a Rpi:

STEP 1
Creat RSA keys for ssh automatic connection to the Rpi
http://www.jscape.com/blog/setting-up-sftp-public-key-authentication-command-line

STEP 2
Set-up the shell script to exchange files between Rpi and main computer
EpSentinel_exchange.sh
Add it to your "application at start-up"

STEP 3
Copy EpSentinel files to your Rpi (EpSentinel.py//EpSource.py//EpConf.py) - EpConf to be modified to suit your installation 
Add the cron job "rpi_crontab.txt" on your Rpi



